100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">MCCAIG</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The Fed recently <a href=\"https://www.federalreserve.gov/aboutthefed/files/quarterly-report-20241122.pdf\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://www.federalreserve.gov/aboutthefed/files/quarterly-report-20241122.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">released</a> its financial statements for the third quarter. In this article, we're looking at the regulator\u2019s balance sheet and the fact that the Fed was not apparently able to forecast its own financial position.</p> <p>The regulator's interest</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1473080351/image_1473080351.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743403-the-fed-was-blindsided-by-its-200-billion-loss", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 16:00:00"}, {"id": "4743859", "title": "Allspring Intermediate Tax/AMT-Free Fund Q3 2024 Commentary", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/680354062/image_680354062.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"money and ink pen on tax form\" data-id=\"680354062\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/680354062/image_680354062.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/680354062/image_680354062.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/680354062/image_680354062.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/680354062/image_680354062.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/680354062/image_680354062.jpg?io=getty-c-w64