io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358108003/image_1358108003.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358108003/image_1358108003.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358108003/image_1358108003.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358108003/image_1358108003.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358108003/image_1358108003.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358108003/image_1358108003.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Lacheev</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Amid the voracious rally in the stock market that has lifted almost every industry to new heights, there has been a major holdout in the internet sector: Match (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MTCH\" title=\"Match Group, Inc.\">MTCH</a></span>), the largest portfolio of dating apps and the parent</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1358108003/image_1358108003.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743835-match-there-may-be-hope-with-rebound-in-tinder-payers-and-a-new-capital-returns-plan-rating-upgrade", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 15:45:26"}, {"id": "4743832", "title": "2 Ideal Buys From 50 'Safer' Dividends In 100 December Sustainables", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170026993/image_2170026993.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"two funny dogs in Christmas decorat