}, {"id": "4743608", "title": "Dividend Dynasty: My Blueprint For Market-Beating Returns", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173198842/image_173198842.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Gold and Currency\" data-id=\"173198842\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"4368px\" height=\"2912px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173198842/image_173198842.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173198842/image_173198842.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173198842/image_173198842.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173198842/image_173198842.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173198842/image_173198842.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173198842/image_173198842.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173198842/image_173198842.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173198842/image_173198842.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">GeorgePeters</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p>On December 10, I wrote an <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743078-the-2-worst-mistakes-dividend-investors-keep-making\">article</a> titled <em>\u201cThe 2 Worst Mistakes Dividend Investors Keep Making.\u201d </em></p> <p>Mistake number one was the risks that come with chasing yield. Essentially, (starting) investors make the mistake of looking for the highest yields, believing the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173198842/image_173198842.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743608-dividend-dynasty-my-blueprint-for-market-beating-returns", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 15:30:00"}, {"id": "4743848", "title": "Allspring High Yield Municipal Bond Fund Q3 2024 Commentary", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1423162084/image_1423162084.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Stacks of coins with inscription BONDS as a concept for investing and saving\" data-id=\"1423162084\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1423162084/image_1423162084.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1423162084/image_1423162084.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1423162084/image_1423162084.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1423162084/image_1423162084.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1423162084/image_1423162084.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1423162084/image_1423162084.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1423162084/image_1423162084.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1423162084/image_1423162084.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">marketlan/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcapti